    <body>
        <section name="Introduction">
            <p>
                MyDoggy-Examples contains some examples to see MyDoggy in action.
            </p>

            <subsection name="MyDoggySet">
                <table>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <img src="./images/mydoggyset.png" alt="MyDoggySet" border="0" hspace="18"/>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p>
                                    <a href="mydoggyset.html">MyDoggySet</a>
                                    is a sample application to see in action many functionalities of MyDoggy.
                                    You can modify tool window properties, show or hide groups and manage main window's
                                    contents.
                                    <br/>
                                    Launch
                                    <a href="./jnlp/mydoggyset/mydoggyset.jnlp">MyDoggySet</a>
                                    using Java Web Start.
                                    <br/>
                                    On Windows Platform to see the transparency in action you have to
                                    <a href="./../download.html">download</a>
                                    a mydoggy distribution.
                                </p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </subsection>

            <subsection name="SampleApp">
                <table>
                    <tbody>
