                                <p>
                                    SampleApp is the result of the
                                    <a href="./../tutorial/tutorial.html">tutorial</a>
                                    based on the
                                    <a href="./../mydoggy-plaf/index.html">default implementation</a>
                                    of mydoggy.
                                </p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
